description:
"Nanobot" a change from a lion, this robot has a weapon in the form of its roar can be heard as far as 100 kilometers. Can you imagine how frightened the lion's prey is when you hear the loud sound?

This robot's top speed is usually used only for short-range attacks, so it must approach the enemy first (silently) before launching an attack.

and The vision of this robot at night is 10 times better than existing robots.

keep up with the excitement of the Robotezos story and roadmap, on the official twitter account: https://twitter.com/robotezos and don't forget our NFT collection. who will mint with 1000 supply, and many other surprises.
